  "text": "The use of crude vegetal extracts on biosensors is a trend due to its analytical specificity, fast and reproducible analysis and excellent activity levels. Moreover, these enzymatic extracts have an extremely low cost, when compared to isolated enzymes. In this context, PPO-containing extracts are optimal for phenolic pollutant assessment [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
